I just spent a bit of time trying to debug why some users in the default service-desk-agents group could not see the Create button, while others could. The ultimate solution was to add this group to be included in the "Service Desk Team" role, but I am remiss to understand why this is not the default. 

Thanks for a great product!

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Service Desk Cloud*. Using *JIRA Service Desk Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSDSERVER-2159].
