Our customers shouldn't need to create an account. We want to use JIRA to manage our issues but we don't want our customers to use JIRA.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
*NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Service Management Cloud*. Using *JIRA Service Management Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSDSERVER-2157].
{panel}
{quote}I think that at this moment reporting in Jira don't give user to much possibility to customize reports. There should be more reports to choose from or functionality to choose what kind of information should be visible in report. I think that lack of this type of functionality is a big problem in JIRA Service Management.
{quote}
More customization features without having to rely on third party plugins like eazyBi.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Service Desk Cloud*. Using *JIRA Service Desk Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSDSERVER-2150].
